<Column name="Accumulated_fair_value_changes_of_the_exposure_due_to_credit_risk" id="56FB2598-03C5-F6E2-49D5-282FEC6ABC0B">
<createdBy>nuvolia</createdBy>
<createdTime>2025-11-05 09:54:54 UTC</createdTime>
<comment><![CDATA[Accumulated changes in fair value due to credit risk in accordance with Part 2.46 of Annex V to Implementing Regulation (EU) No 680/2014 of the exposure that is derecognised because of the Property, plant and equipment taken into possession.

Note: This amount must only be reported when it is negative.]]></comment>
